headline: Barclays raises price target on Ulta Beauty at $445
summary: Investing.com -- Barclays raised its price target on Ulta Beauty Inc (NASDAQ:ULTA) to $445 from $410 on stronger-than-expected preliminary fourth-quarter results and the appointment of Kecia Steelman as the company's new CEO.
